title: Volodymyr Chesnakov
text: Volodymyr Hennadiyovych Chesnakov (; born 12 February 1988) is a <a href="professional">professional</a> <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> who plays for <a href="FC%20Vorskla%20Poltava">Vorskla Poltava</a> in the <a href="Ukrainian%20Premier%20League">Ukrainian Premier League</a>.
